&lt;h2 id="overview"&gt;Overview&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This study presents a novel method for creating moving thermal sensations by integrating the thermal referral illusion with tactile motion. Three experiments on human forearms identify speed thresholds for perceived thermal motion and validate the approach in VR interaction scenarios. Published in &lt;strong&gt;UIST 2024&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>